<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Express.js Kusto Service</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>


    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
        }

        html,
        body {
            display: block;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='40' height='40' viewBox='0 0 40 40' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='%2300ff88' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Cpath d='M20 20c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16s-16 7.163-16 16 7.163 16 16 16 16-7.163 16-16zm16 0c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16s-16 7.163-16 16 7.163 16 16 16 16-7.163 16-16z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            animation: float 25s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(2deg); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1); }
        }

        .main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .main {
                padding: 3rem;
            }
        }

        .content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ff88, #00b4d8);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3);
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00ff88, #00b4d8, #00ff88);
            border-radius: 18px;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: borderGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes borderGlow {
            0% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .logo i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #0f0f23;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .heading {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
            color: #00ff88;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.5);
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .heading {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .heading {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #64ffda;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.7s both;
        }

        .service-url {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #00ff88;
            word-break: break-all;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1);
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.8s both;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 1s both;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border-color: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #00ff88;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #64ffda;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .button-container {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 1.2s both;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-flex;
            height: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.4);
            padding: 0 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #64ffda;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1);
            border-color: #00ff88;
            color: #00ff88;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3);
        }

        .button:focus-visible {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3);
        }

        .button:disabled {
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .button.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ff88, #00b4d8);
            border: none;
            color: #0f0f23;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .button.primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00e676, #0288d1);
            color: #0f0f23;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.4);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.6);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 1.4s both;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1);
        }

        /* 반응형 스타일 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .heading {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .button-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.75rem;
            }
            
            .button {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
            }
        }

    </style>

    <div class="container">
        <main class="main">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="logo-container">
                    <div class="logo">
                        <i class="fas fa-terminal"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h1 class="heading">Express.js-Kusto</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Framework</p>
                <p class="tagline">엔터프라이즈급 TypeScript 백엔드 프레임워크</p>
                
                <% if (typeof FRAMEWORK_URL !== 'undefined' && FRAMEWORK_URL) { %>
                    <div class="service-url">
                        <i class="fas fa-link" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>
                        <%= FRAMEWORK_URL %>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                        <h3>혁신적 아키텍처</h3>
                        <p>파일 기반 자동 등록<br/>멀티 데이터베이스 관리</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <h3>완전 타입 안전</h3>
                        <p>Injectable DI<br/>타입 안전 의존성 주입</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                        <h3>제로 코드 자동화</h3>
                        <p>CRUD 자동 생성<br/>REST API + 문서화</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                        <h3>고급 개발 환경</h3>
                        <p>Webpack 빌드<br/>프로덕션 최적화</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-magic"></i>
                        <h3>Import-Free 구조</h3>
                        <p>injected/repo/db<br/>자동 주입</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-vial"></i>
                        <h3>테스트 자동 생성</h3>
                        <p>보안 테스트 포함<br/>실시간 대시보드</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="button-container">
                    <% if (typeof NODE_ENV !== 'undefined' && NODE_ENV === 'development') { %>
                        <a href="/docs" class="button primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-book" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            Documentation
                        </a>
                        <a href="/docs/dev" class="button">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            Dashboard
                        </a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>MIT License &copy; 2025 Express.js-Kusto Framework</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.7rem;">🚀 개발 속도 3배 향상 • ⚡ 팀 협업 효율성 극대화 • 🛡️ 유지보수성 혁신적 개선</p>
        </footer>
    </div>


</body>

</html>